  },
  "things_not_to_do": [
    "Don't write hex literals (#3b82f6) in components.",
    "Don't write color: white as a default on a class that may sit on a light background.",
    "Don't assume non-curated shade stops (e.g. 400, 800) have Tailwind classes — use var() for those.",
    "Don't duplicate semantic classes inside <style scoped> when a Tailwind utility exists."
  ]
